    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Mummius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fab</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Ancyra <lb n="3"/>miles <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXXVI <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>stipend</abbr><ex>iorum</ex></expan> XVI <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Arma bis octonis felicia qui tulit annis <lb n="2"/>hic situs est fato Mummius ipse suo <lb n="3"/>si sapiunt obiti data munera percipis <expan><abbr>am</abbr><ex>pla</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>et recipis nostrae pignus amicitiae <lb n="5"/>hoc tibi cum titulo posuit Cornelius Chrestus <lb n="6"/>et dixit lachrymans <note>sic</note> sit tibi ter<expan><ex>r</ex><abbr>a</abbr></expan> levis </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Cornelius <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Chrestus pos<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>it</abbr></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Drei Texte auf drei voneinander abgesetzten Inschriftfeldern der Vorderseite. Der Anfangsbuchstabe L der ersten Inschrift erstreckt sich vertikal auf drei Zeilen.</p>
